{"tid":559029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日地鐵傳讓座風波 6旬翁拿刀怒捅未讓座年輕人","createTime":"2018-02-12T22:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T04:18:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"754fdb5a2c9640a5e2fc19c4277312dbdd0f0762","tid":559029,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpqGicOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpqGicOV.jpg&h=1fa6506a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本地鐵日前傳出一起攻擊事件。6旬翁拿刀怒捅未讓座年輕人。（即時新聞組攝）<br />\n2018-02-12 17:11<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國內外許多交通運輸工具上都有設置博愛座，優先讓老弱婦孺坐。不過日本一位老人最近卻因為不滿年輕人沒讓座，於是拿出刀械攻擊對方，遭警方逮捕。<br />\n綜合日媒報導，日本大阪7日發生一起攻擊事件，一位62歲老人在大阪搭乘地鐵時，看到一位34歲男子一直坐在優先座（類似台灣博愛座）上沒讓座，於是心生不滿。老人隨後拿出隨身攜帶的水果刀刺進未讓座男子的腹部，造成該男子重傷，事後老人遭日本警方以殺人未遂罪嫌逮捕。<br />\n報導指出，日本在2015年也曾發生類似情形，當時一位71歲老人不滿另一位50歲男子在優先座附近滑平板，於是拿出菜刀意圖攻擊對方，最後遭逮捕。"},{"pid":"716b15439b49a11880851e5d2bc51dfc63f3dd4a","tid":559029,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340571&d=naZqUvrmHkgCcgPIqat5xpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=9316d950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340571&h=d6ed96ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340571</a>"},{"pid":"540db7b2541e562a40b4cef1fcccf6d4bd99ba71","tid":559029,"uid":70183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"邊度都有廢老<br />\n<br />\n明明以前無關愛座啲人都會讓座<br />\n<br />\n而家有左反而多左衝突"},{"pid":"0def9a8a682851aeceef13f6e71296b6ac9b31bc","tid":559029,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T23:19:14